\par }{\b\insrsid14827227\charrsid14827227 Man Student:}{\insrsid14827227\charrsid8943298  Professor James?
\par }{\insrsid14827227 
\par }{\b\insrsid14827227\charrsid14827227 Woman Professor:}{\insrsid14827227\charrsid8943298  Yes.
\par }{\insrsid14827227 
\par }{\b\insrsid14827227\charrsid14827227 Man Student:}{\insrsid14827227\charrsid8943298  I was told that I should talk to you about . . . well, I'm interested in switching majors and I wanted some advice.
\par }{\insrsid14827227 
\par }{\b\insrsid14827227\charrsid14827227 Woman Professor:}{\insrsid14827227\charrsid8943298  OK. So I assume you're switching to a degree in linguistics. Could you give me some background on your previous studies?
\par }{\insrsid14827227 
\par }{\b\insrsid14827227\charrsid14827227 Man Student:}{\insrsid14827227\charrsid8943298  Yeah, I was studying speech pathology, specializing in phonological disorders. But}{\insrsid1966817 ,}{\insrsid14827227\charrsid8943298 
 I went to Peru last summer, and, well, I ran out of money}{\insrsid1966817 ,}{\insrsid14827227\charrsid8943298  and to pay for my expenses, I did some English teaching}{\insrsid1966817 ,}{\insrsid14827227\charrsid8943298  and I really enjoyed it.
\par }{\insrsid14827227 
\par }{\b\insrsid14827227\charrsid14827227 Woman Professor:}{\insrsid14827227\charrsid8943298  OK, um, so are you thinking about a degree in applied linguistics?
\par }{\insrsid14827227 
\par }{\b\insrsid14827227\charrsid14827227 Man Student:}{\insrsid14827227\charrsid8943298  Well, yeah, you know, with my background in phonology, I was able to help people improve their pronunciation}{\insrsid1966817 ,}{\insrsid14827227\charrsid8943298 
 and I thought that perhaps I'd be more interested in that aspect of language.
\par }{\insrsid14827227 
\par }{\b\insrsid14827227\charrsid14827227 Woman Professor:}{\insrsid14827227\charrsid8943298  OK. Well}{\insrsid1966817 ,}{\insrsid14827227\charrsid8943298  some of your courses will probably fulfill linguistic requirements, and many of them will be
 advantageous for you as far as the knowledge is concerned, but not necessarily for course transfer.
\par }{\insrsid14827227 
\par }{\b\insrsid14827227\charrsid14827227 Man Student:}{\insrsid14827227\charrsid8943298  OK.
\par }{\insrsid14827227 
\par }{\b\insrsid14827227\charrsid14827227 Woman Professor:}{\insrsid14827227\charrsid8943298  Let me find our, oh}{\insrsid1966817 ,}{\insrsid14827227\charrsid8943298 
